			<h2>Welcome to HireTech Help & Support</h2>
			<p>Here you can find answers to common questions and get in touch
				with our support team for further assistance.</p>

			<div class="common-questions">
				<h2>Common Questions</h2>
				<div>
					<h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
					<p>To create an account, click on the "register as jobseeker"
						button on the homepage and fill out the required information.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>How do I reset my password?</h3>
					<p>To reset your password, click on the "Forgot Password" link
						on the login page and follow the instructions.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>How do I update my profile information?</h3>
					<p>To update your profile information, log in to your account
						and go to the "MyProfile" section.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>How do I contact support?</h3>
					<p>You can contact support by emailing us at
						support@hiretech.com or calling 9346789783.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3>What should I do if I encounter an error?</h3>
					<p>If you encounter an error, try refreshing the page or
						clearing your browser cache. If the problem persists, contact
						support.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="contact-info">
				<h2>Contact HireTech Support</h2>
				<p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please
					reach out to our support team:</p>
				<p>Email: support@hiretech.com</p>
				<p>Phone: 9346789783</p>
				<p>Our support team is available Monday to Friday, 9 AM to 5 PM.</p>
			</div>
